Main Research Areas
A. End-to-End Learned Compression
Entire codec jointly optimized.

Loss function:
L=R+λD
Where:
R = bitrate
D = distortion

B. Perceptual Optimization

Optimize:
Human visual quality
instead of only PSNR.

Metrics:
MS-SSIM
LPIPS
VMAF-like perceptual models

C. Learned Entropy Models
Neural probability estimation improves coding efficiency.

D. Semantic Compression

Transmit:
Important visual meaning
instead of exact pixels.
Future-oriented research.

